 {
  "text": "Hi, my name is Lucas. Let me tell you all about me. I am from Rio de Janeiro, but now I live in Sao Paulo. My family is big. I have two brothers and one sister. My favorite hobby is playing soccer. I also like reading books at night. I am a friendly person, and I love meeting new people. Nice to meet you!",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a8_listening_lucas_aboutme.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hello, my name is Marina. I want to tell you about me. My hometown is Curitiba. I have a small family: my mother, my father, and me. I have a pet, a little dog. My favorite thing is cooking with my mother on Sunday. I am a happy and nice person. I like meeting new friends. What about you?",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a8_listening_marina_aboutme.mp3"
 },
